Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their shape and abilities are\Nbased on their Soul Reaper's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.56,0:00:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers gain power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by learning their names\Nand synergizing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are born with Soul Reapers\Nand die with Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what Zanpakuto are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! He's been awakened!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What Spiritual Pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been sealed away\Nfor so long…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet he still possesses\Nthis much Spiritual Pressure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've awakened… Koga…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've waited for this moment\Nfor so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time for us\Nto complete our goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mura…masa…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:03:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga must be tied up in prison\Nfeeling pretty humiliated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It totally serves him right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to boast so\Nproudly of his power…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could see how dejected\Nhe looks with my own eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first heard of this plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had my doubts about\Nwhether it would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he fell for it\Nhook, line and sinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over for him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:03:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K…Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the interruption!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! Third Seat Kuchiki broke out\Nof the barrack jailhouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed the three Soul Reapers\Ninvolved in that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…when I think back,\Nit still makes my blood boil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for us to forget…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those men are no longer around.\NThey're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use this opportunity\Nto forget our past karma
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and live our lives looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Ginrei…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what I have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still…I believed that they felt\Nashamed about betraying me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing them…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still didn't make\Nthe empty feeling in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of knowing that they tricked\Nand deceived me go away…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I…\Nsupposed to do…now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've completely lost any chance\Nof proving your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had reflected\Non your situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,conducted yourself properly and\Nconfined yourself to quarters
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the moment suspicion\Nwas cast on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything would have\Nbeen all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confine myself? Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do anything…\Nthat is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may have had good cause,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you committed\Na grave crime of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,killing men who did\Nnot draw their swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will likely be put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am well aware of\Nyour superior abilities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, you still\Nlack the heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to make full use\Nof those abilities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your overconfidence\Nbrought about this result.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do not forget that you now bear{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the title and responsibility\Nof our clan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ginrei…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same.\NYou're just like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You act like you're on my side…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You befriend me…\Nput me off my guard…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in your heart…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…you're just jealous of my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whisper…Muramasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ginrei! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't close your heart!\NUndo that barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save killing you for last.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are tons of people\NI want to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga… Koga…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is your soul\Nso agitated?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all enemies, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill them before they kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing what's\Nnecessary to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forget about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you live your life\Nlooking forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I so hated?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I am powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga! Let's create a new world.\NI'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it this power that's\Ncausing the harm…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my power…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whisper…Muramasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muramasa, release!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:11:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have news to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga's victims now exceed\Nseveral dozen as of yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Koga's unique abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,selecting even veteran\Nsquad members is meaningless
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because their swords\Nget taken away…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to take on\NKoga's illusion-type Zanpakuto
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is to understand his power\Nand close one's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in order to block\Nhis attack in that state,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one must possess\Nconsiderable Spiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and an unyielding\Nmental fortitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from myself, if there is\None other person who could,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on top of all that,\Nstill cross swords with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we might have a chance…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will help you seal Koga away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you kill even innocent\Npeople in the Rukon District?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…that's because…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to send a message\Nto all of the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A message? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To show the foolishness of\Nostracizing me from this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to show how powerless the Soul\NReapers are to stop my power…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To do that, you indiscriminately\Nkill defenseless people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that necessary to create\Nour vision of an ideal new world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Our"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "our"?!\NWho're you kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You consider yourself my equal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sword should keep quiet\Nand do as it's told!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're exhausted…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should rest…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a sword—\Ndon't give me orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you two\Nsenior citizens here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to kneel down\Nbefore my power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem that's\Nnot the reason…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't your power for the purpose\Nof making your ideal come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no ideals in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that exists beyond ideals
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the despair of being unable\Nto make them come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But despair releases\Nmy true power…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despair is what\Ntakes off my binding
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and frees my heart\Nto do as it wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga…you're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those with power\Ncreate all order…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that power is\Ndark black and ugly,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if that power wins, black becomes\Nthe color of what is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless, Ginrei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fellow is possessed\Nby power—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he no longer hears\Nwhat you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to cut down\Nthe two of you one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ginrei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to fight me\Nwith your heart sealed off again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use all of\Nyour strength that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hainawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your powers better than\Nanyone here in the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:16:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whisper…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muramasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muramasa! Appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release! Can't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!\NWhy won't you appear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Koga seems unable to use Muramasa.\N– Muramasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Genryusai, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Ginrei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shisokeppu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muramasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muramasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:18:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga… Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't answer me…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was on the verge \Nof being sealed away,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called for you…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called…for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You refused to lend me a hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you…called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice did not reach me…\NIt's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited so long\Nfor you to call me…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I was called,\NI would have come at any time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to assist you with\Nall the power within me…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is how I felt…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for so long,\Nyour voice never called…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, I learned that\Nyou had been sealed away…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've been\Ntrying for so long…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to undo the seal…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's meaningless if you're\Nnot there when I need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, a Soul Reaper,\Ngave birth to your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you need to do\Nis to do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't we of one spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"One spirit"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, you're just a sword…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing more than a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mere tool shouldn't\Nbe so conceited!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call your own Zanpakuto\Na tool and slay it…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to\Ncall yourself a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muramasa's objective was Koga,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.82,0:23:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Koga stabbed him,\Nand then Byakuya appeared…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.35,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So…huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time,\NSenbonzakura will explain it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so even a monkey\Nwould understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.85,0:23:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can confirm\Nyour facts at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I'd expect from you,\NBrother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being\Nso considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he takes us for fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'm going to\Nexplain this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.07,0:23:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kenseikan is a headpiece
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.07,0:23:49.07,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,KENSEIKAN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that only high-ranking nobles\Nare permitted to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be wearing it someday,\Nas well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.60,0:23:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start thinking about\Nhow you'll wear yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.55,0:23:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I might ask, Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.55,0:23:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:24:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you wear your kenseikan,\NGrandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.90,0:24:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.02,0:24:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,